| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7326 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9f3a9e32-1b93-5cf2-81ab-2eaf69d1c85a"
